    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1943-12-20T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1943-12-20T00:00:00-05:00" n="523"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d523">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">
                    <persName corresp="#p_RFD1">Roosevelt</persName> Papers: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Ambassador in the Soviet Union</hi> (<persName
                        corresp="#p_HK1" type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Harriman</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">President</gloss>
                    </hi>
                    <note n="1" xml:id="d523fn1">Sent by the United States Naval Attaché Moscow, via
                        Navy channels.</note>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#left">
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">secret</hi>
                    </seg>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Moscow</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1943-12-20">20 December
                            1943</date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Personal and secret for the President from <persName corresp="#p_HK1"
                        >Harriman</persName>.</p>
                <p>At the Teheran Conference you and the Prime Minister agreed that the Italian
                    ships requested by the Soviets should be delivered on one February.<note n="2"
                        xml:id="d523fn2">See <hi rend="italic">ante</hi>, <ref target="#pg_597">p.
                            597</ref>.</note> Request that I be informed of the action taken to
                    carry out this commitment as I shall undoubtedly be queried by <persName
                        corresp="#p_MVM1">Molotov</persName> at a meeting with him scheduled for
                    Friday or Saturday<note n="3" xml:id="d523fn3">December 24 or 25.</note> to
                    discuss unfinished business of Teheran.</p>
            </div>
        </body>
